---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = '/Diary';
---

<BaseLayout title="首頁">
  <section>
    <h1>Main</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">記錄每天成長了多少，持之以恆的記錄</p>

    <article>
      <time>2026 年 7 月 1 日</time>
      <h3>
        <a href={`${base}/posts/2026-07-01`} class="post-title-link">新的開始</a>
      </h3>
      <p>
        決定用這個 Repo 來記錄自己的每一天，像是一本專屬的日記本。... 
        <a href={`${base}/posts/2026-07-01`} class="read-more">閱讀全文 →</a>
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <style>
    .post-title-link {
      color: var(--color-text);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .post-title-link:hover {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .read-more {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      margin-left: 0.4rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .read-more:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
